      '<ul>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">The hospital has 400 plus full time doctors, 12 centres of excellence and 40 specialities.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Artemis Hospital has many different centres of excellence including Artemis Emergency &amp; Trauma Centre, Artemis Heart Centre, Artemis Cancer Centre, Artemis Neurosciences Centre, Artemis Joint Replacement &amp; Orthopaedics, Centre, Artemis Minimally Invasive &amp; Bariatric Surgery, Centre, Artemis Transplant Centre (Liver, Kidney, Cornea &amp; Bone Marrow Transplant), Artemis Women &amp; Child Centre, Artemis Pulmonologist &amp; Critical Care Centre, Artemis Gastro sciences Centre, Artemis Cosmetology &amp; Plastic Surgery Centre, Artemis Pain Medicine &amp; Palliative care.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Artemis Hospital provides good level of comfort during the stay including TV in room, private rooms, Free Wi-Fi, &nbsp;Phone in Room, Mobility accessible rooms, Family accommodation, Laundry, Safe in the room, Nursery / Nanny services, Dry cleaning, Personal assistance / Concierge, Religious facilities, Fitness Caf&eacute; , Business centre services.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Some of the transportation services provided by the hospital include Airport pickup, Local transportation booking, Visa / Travel office, Car Hire, Air ambulance.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">The hospital possesses the latest medical equipment such as, 3 Tesla MRI, 64 Slice Cardiac CT Scan &amp; 16 slice PET CT from Philips Medical System.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">The cafeteria of the hospital offers cuisine from every part of the globe with all time dining facility. You can also order a diet on request which means your food will be customised according to your needs. </span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">There&rsquo;s a service of Health insurance coordination, Medical travel insurance, Foreign currency exchange, ATM Credit Card, Debit Card, Net banking.</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Pre-departure, Post admission &amp; Post Discharge services are provided to the international patients. </span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">Some of the other services provided by Artemis Hospital are Executive Health Checks, Workplace clinics for counselling, Outpatient and hospitalisation services, Healthcare education and awareness programs, First Aid and BLS Training, Emergency Services, Organisational Healthcare Audit.</span></p>\r\n',
