      '<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">BLK hospital is a Set up originally in 1956 as a 200-bed hospital in Delhi by an eminent Obstetrician and Gynaecologist, Dr. B.L. Kapoor, BLK-Max Super Speciality Hospital was redeveloped and re-launched as a 650 bed Multi Super Speciality facility with a vision to create a tertiary healthcare organisation focused on patients and non-intrusive quality care utilising leading edge technology with a touch of humans. Now, it is the largest private sector hospital in Delhi, India. The mission is to achieve professional excellence in quality care and to ensure care with ethics and integrity and to deliver the highest standard of healthcare. The hospital has the finest doctors, state-of-the-art infrastructure, cutting edge medicine and nursing with a smile.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Specialisation </strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Multiple Centres of Excellence have been established by the hospital which include Cancer Centre, Centre for Bone Marrow Transplant, Heart Centre, Centre for Neurosciences, Institute for Digestive &amp; Liver Diseases, Centre for Renal Sciences &amp; Kidney Transplant, Institute for Bone, Joint Replacement, Orthopaedics Spine &amp; Sports Medicine, Centre for Chest &amp; Respiratory Diseases, Centre for Plastic &amp; Cosmetic Surgery, Centre for Child Health and Centre for Critical Care.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Locality</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">BLK Super Speciality Hospital is located at Pusa road, Radha SoamiSatsang, Rajendra Place,New Delhi110005. From the Indira Gandhi International Airport, the hospital is a 18 minute drive with a distance of 12.3 kilometres and from the Rajendra Place Station, which is the nearest metro station600 meters away, it is just a 3 minute drive. Hotel Le Sancy, at a distance of 550 meters isjust 3 minutes away from the hospital. Hotel Megha Sheraton andHotel Panicker&rsquo;s Residency are also located nearby. The Dhaba Junction, Omelettes - A Multi Cuisine Restaurant, Raffles Restaurant and Bikaner vala are nearby located restaurants. The Red Fort, India Gate, Jantar Mantar, Sulabh International Museum Of Toilets, Lotus Temple and the National Zoological Park are the tourist attractions near the hospital. You can also explore the Moments Mall and the Spark Mall. </span></p>\r\n',
