      '<p style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital, Saket is a 250 bedded multi-speciality tertiary care hospital. It is owned and operated by the Max Healthcare Group which is promoted and led by Abhay Soi. Their vision is to be the most well regarded healthcare provider in India and to remain committed to the highest standards of clinical excellence and patient care, supported by latest technology and cutting edge research. The hospital uses world class technologies like the CUSA machine, Da Vinci Xi Robotic System, Endoscopic Ultrasound (EUS), Femtosecond Laser Platform, Intra-Operative &amp; Portable CT scanner with Navigation, Remote Monitoring System, Single Head Gamma Camera with SPECT, Stereotactic Body Radiation Therapy</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">SBRT, Transcranial Doppler and TrueReam linac with Exactrac. The Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital offers procedures like Gastric Bypass, Lap Gastric Banding, Sleeve Gastrectomy, Atrial Septal Defect (ASD) Repair, Angiography (Including Non-Ionic Contrast)</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Angioplasty, Bentall Procedure, cosmetic procedures like Dermal Fillers, Ear Correction, Ear Surgery (Pinnaplasty), Face Lift (Face and Neck), Facial Feminization Surgery, ENT procedures including Laryngectomy, Nasal, Polyp Surgery, Septoplasty, Tympanoplasty and Gynaecology procedures like C-Section, Fibroid, Removal Surgery, Normal Delivery and Polycystic Ovarian Syndrome (PCOS) Treatment along with a whole range of other treatments as well.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Specialisation </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">The Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital provides excellence in above 22 centres which include Bariatric Surgery / Metabolic, Cancer Care / Oncology, Gastroenterology, Hepatology &amp; Endoscopy, Laparoscopic / Minimal Access Surgery, Neurosciences, Surgical Gastroenterology, Bone Marrow Transplant, Endocrinology &amp; Diabetes, Kidney Transplant, Liver Transplant and Biliary Sciences, Orthopaedics &amp; Joint Replacement, Urology, Cardiac Arrhythmia, Dermatology, Electrophysiology- Pacemaker, Eye Care, Health And Wellness, Internal Medicine, Interventional Radiology, Mental Health And Behavioural Sciences, Nutrition And Dietetics, Paediatric (Ped), Physiotherapy &amp;, Rehabilitation Medicine, Podiatry, Radiology, Audiology And Speech Therapy, Dental Care, Ear Nose Throat, Emergency &amp; Trauma, Gastro intestinal &amp; Hepatopancreatobiliary Surgical Oncology, Infertility &amp; IVF, Interventional Cardiology, Lung Transplant, Nephrology</p>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Obstetrics And Gynaecology, Pain Management, Plastic Surgery (Aesthetic And Reconstructive Surgery), Pulmonology andThoracic Surgery.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Locality </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital is located at Press Enclave Road, Saket Institutional Area, Saket, Mandir Marg, New Delhi, Delhi, 110017, India. The Indira Gandhi International Airport is the nearest to the hospital with a distance of 12.6 kilometres which takes around 25 minutes to cover. The Malviya Nagar subway station is the nearest metro station just 800 metres from the hospital which is a 3 minute drive only. Hotel Ambica Inn, Svelte Hotel &amp; Personal Suites and Country Inn &amp; Suites by Radisson, Delhi Saket are nearby located hotels for stay. Tourist attractions to explore nearby include The Garden of Five Senses, Khirki Masjid, Shri Jhulelal Mandir, Jama Masjid Saket and the Pragati Park. Nearest malls include MGF Metropolitan Mall, Mall Fountain, Select Citywalk and Square One Mall.</p>\r\n',
