    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital was awarded with the Best Hospital Mother &amp; Child Care (North) by the ET Healthworld Hospital Awards.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The ET Fertility Awards awarded Max Super Speciality Hospital with the BEST INTEGRATED CARE AWARD (QUATERNARY CARE) (NATIONAL).</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital was awarded with Health Innovation of the Year by the Max Bike Responder.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Max Super Speciality Hospital, A Unit of Max Healthcare Institute Limited &amp; Max Super Speciality Hospital, A Unit of Devki Devi Foundation, Saket (New Delhi, India) was recognized with the GOLD SEAL- JOINT COMMISSION INTERNATIONAL, on 18th February, 2017.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital offers a 250 bed facility along with 12 high-end modular operation theatres.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital at Saket also has an emergency resuscitation, and observation unit, 72 critical care beds, 18 HDU beds, a dedicated endoscopy unit, and an advanced dialysis unit.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The tertiary care hospital is equipped with 256 Slice CT Angio and a 3.0 Tesla digital broad band MRI.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">They also have Cath Labs with electrophysiology navigation, and a ?at panel C-Arm detector.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has the help of over 300 leading specialist Doctors, a strong nursing staff, and state-of-the-art innovative medical tools.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital provides the advantage ofintegrated medical care in a multidisciplinary setting provided by a faculty of highly qualified doctors, nurses, &amp; healthcare professionals.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">They also have a dedicated appointment line and query support. Also they have dedicated coordinators for managing Immigration check-ups.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has NABL approved labs and certified Radiologists.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Max Smart Super Speciality Hospital has highly developed and certified lab services for TB and Sputum testing.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has air ambulance service available at one call of +91 11 4055 4055 which is accessible from cell phones and land lines. The service ensures the safest and most secure shifting to our hospital or medical centres located across India. They have a special trained team of doctor/nurse who accompany the patient through the transfer. Portable life saving equipment like defibrillators, ventilators, infusion pumps, spine board, balloon pumps, pacemakers, monitors, oxygen cylinders, stretchers and other special requirements are available in the aircraft.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Surface ambulance is also available in cases of emergency at a call of011 4055 4055 with state of the art medical equipment like cardiac monitors, defibrillator, airway equipment etc. transport ventilator is also available for transport of intubated and ventilated patients.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">They also have GE Light speed 16-slice CT scanners, Interventional Radiology Suite, X-rays and the Novalis Tx - a highly powerful radiosurgery system, which offers a combination of advanced technology for the treatment of tumours and other body parts.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital also uses the Allegretto Wave Eye-Q excimer laser, which uses technical innovations to get laser vision correction, with excellent clinical results.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
