    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital received the AHPI Healthcare Excellence Award 2019 in Nursing Excellence and Quality beyond Accreditation.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Apollo Hospitals received these Hospital Management Awards (HMA) - Gold award for Community Involvement Compassion Courage Hope- Rebuilding Livelihood; Gold award for Mobile and Online Services Urbanization of Patient Transportation; Excellence award for Facility Management and Financial Improvement P2P &ndash; From Panic to Peace-Clinical Alarm Safety Campaign; Excellence award for Hospital Chief Executive Officer of the Year Apollo Ring of Care.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Praxis Media Private Limited, NATIONAL QUALITY EXCELLENCE AWARDS, 2017 Times critical care 2017 has ranked Indraprastha Apollo among 10 best in Cardiac sciences, Gastroenterology, Obstetrics and gynaecology, Paediatrics, Neurosciences, Nephrology, Urology, Oncology, Emergency and trauma.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">It has been ranked as the Best Indian Hospital for Medical Travel and Best Organ Transplant centre at ASSOCHAM- Med travel 2017, New Delhi on 21st February 2017.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has received excellence awards in Prevention of Medical Equipment from Environmental impact &ndash; Bio Medical Facilities Improvement (Biomedical Department) and in Reducing ALOS- a triumph of teamwork &ndash; Customer Service (MS Office); Transforming Skills into Perfection &ndash; Human Resource Development (Nursing Department).</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">They have also received Express health care award in Alerting the high alert &ndash; Improving the safety of high alert medications has won the Gold Award in the Patient Safety category.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The School health programme Apollo Innovations awards include Alerting the High Alert (Quality), AMDP (Quality), Conservation of Energy and Water (Engineering), Reduction ALOS a triumph of teamwork (DDMS Office), Patient Discharge (Nursing), A healthy Start (Special initiatives), Transforming skills into perfection (Nursing).</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Times Of India Healthcare Survey 2016 ranked Apollo Hospitals Number 1 in Neurosciences, Renal Sciences, Oncology, Paediatrics, Gynaecology and Obstetrics &amp; Emergency in India. According to the survey, the hospital is the 3rd best private multi-speciality hospital in India, Number 1 private hospital in India for Paediatrics, Number 1 private hospital in India for Pulmonologist, Number 1 private hospital in India for Neurology, 2nd best private hospital in India for Oncology, 3rd best private hospital in India for Diabetes, 4th best private hospital in India for Gynaecology, 4th best private hospital in India for Ophthalmology, 4th best private hospital in India for Gastroenterology, 6th best private hospital in India for Cardiology and 7th best private hospital in India for Orthopaedics.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Apollo Hospitals bagged Highly Commended Award At IMTJ Medicine Travels Awards 2015</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital received the Asian Hospital Management Awards (HMA) 2014 at the 13th HMA Conference Singapore</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital also received Excellence Award for &ldquo;Transforming the skill in to perfection&rsquo; Building skill for using medical devices effectively&rdquo; (Bio Medical Equipment / Facilities Improvement Category)</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">An Apollo pharmacy open 24 hours is located in the atrium of the hospital.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">A choice of Patient rooms are available including A/C Multi Bed Units, semi- private units, single room, deluxe room, suite and day care rooms.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Highly skilled and dedicated nurse staffs are available at all times in the hospital, just press the Call Bell near the patient&rsquo;s bed.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Patient Pharmacy is open round the clock to cater to all of your requirements of medicine.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Individualised attention is given to all patients by the dedicated and efficient team of dieticians.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Lockers, cloak room and laundry service is provided by the hospital as well.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">A communication centre and a bank/ATM is present in the Atrium.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
