    about_hospital:
      '<p style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute, New Delhi is a Multi-Speciality hospital acquired by Dr. Parvinder Singh wholed Fortis Healthcare. Established in 1988, Escorts celebrated 25 years of Cardiac excellence in 2013.The hospital has set benchmarks in cardiac care with Paediatric path breaking work over the past 25 years. It is recognised as a centre of excellence providing the latest technology in Cardiac Bypass Surgery, Interventional Cardiology, Non-invasive Cardiology, Paediatric Cardiology and Paediatric Cardiac Surgery. The hospital offers the most advanced laboratories performing complete range of investigative tests in the field of Nuclear Medicine, Radiology, Biochemistry, Haematology, Transfusion Medicine and Microbiology. Fortis Escorts Heart Institute has enriched numerous lives through its world-class treatment and compassionate patient care.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Specialisation </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute has specialised departments for different conditions including Liver &amp; Digestive Diseases Institute, Kidney and Urology Institute, Vascular Surgery, Bone And Joint Institute, Organ Transplant, Minimal Access Bariatric, Gl Surgery &amp; GI, Oncosurgery, General Surgery, Critical Care Medicine, Internal Medicine, Plastic &amp; Cosmetic Surgery, Pulmonology, Diabetology, Endocrinology and Metabolism Diseases, ENT, Ophthalmology- The Sight Avenue, Neuro Surgery &amp; Spine, Rehab Lab, Physiotherapy, Preventive Medicine, Clinical Psychology, Clinical Nutrition and Dietetics, Blood Disorders/ Haematology, Neurology, Rheumatology, Histopathology, Dentistry, Blood Bank, Chronic Total, Occlusion Percutaneous Coronary, Intervention, Mental Health &amp; Behavioural Sciences, Sleep Apnea Insomnia Clinic, Radiology, Nephrology, Nuclear Medicine, Anaesthesiology.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Some of the core specialities of the hospital are Cardiac Sciences - Cardiology (Adult &amp; Paediatric), Gastroenterology, Hepatobiliary &amp; Liver Transplant, Kidney, Urology &amp; Kidney transplant, Bone &amp; Joint, Vascular Interventions.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Critical Care</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute has a dedicated Critical Care department who offers 24x7 care to patients in potentially life-threatening conditions, requiring life support system and other intensive medical interventions. The patients who have any dysfunction or failure of one or more organ systems, like cardiac, pulmonary, neurology, liver and kidney, amongst others are admitted to the Critical Care Unit (CCU).There is an experienced multidisciplinary team which provides state-of-the-art patient care with promptness and compassion. The team comprises of trained, efficient and skilled staff in critical care medicine. The team of doctors and other support professionals are trained at elite medical institutions and have extensive experience in managing all kinds of critical clinical conditions across the age group of patients. The wards are well maintained with high-precision monitoring devices, advanced equipment, high standards of infection control measures and a team of highly specialized critical care experts. The hospital also has trained physicians guided by the senior doctors who are available at the critical care ward round the clock to closely observe the patients with critical illness till they recover.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Locality</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute is situated at Okhla Road, New Delhi, Delhi 110025. It is 18 kilometres away from Indra Gandhi International Airport which takes around 25 minutes to cover by road. The Sukhdev Vihar station is the nearest one to Fortis Escorts Heart Institute. The nearest bus stop to the hospital is Ohkla Extention / Abdul Fazal Enclave. Top rated hotel, Hotel The Suryaa is just 0.4 kilometre from the hospital and Hotel IKON Residency is just 0.3 kilometre away. Hotel Bluestone &ndash; Nehru Place, The Hosteller, The Orion Plaza and The Oakland Plaza are also close to the hospital. Flaming Chilli Pepper, The Village Caf&eacute;, Legends Of Angelica, and Paranthas N More are some of the restaurants which are near the hospital. You can explore ISKCON Temple, Lotus Temple and Kalka Ji Mandir which are close to the hospital. India Gate, Qutub Minar, Naini Lake and Agrasen Ki Baoli are some of the tourist attractions which are near the hospital.</p>\r\n',
