      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Top specialized hospitals list for Cardiology specialty in Newsweek&#39;s Best Hospital 2021.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Gold Award in Healthcare Delivery Brand in IHW Awards 2020.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded the Best Interventional Cardiology&amp; Cardiac Surgery Award in Medical Value Travels Awards 2019.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Excellence in Cardiac Sciences by ABP Healthcare Leadership 2019.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded as the Best Hospital in Cardiology in Times Healthcare Achievers Awards in 2018.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded as the Best Hospital in Cardiology by ICICI Lombard &amp; CNBC TV 18 Healthcare Awards 2015, for the third consecutive year.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded as the Best Cardiology</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Hospital in India by the Week Magazine 2014, 2015, 2016 &amp; 2018.</p>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute offers cutting edge technology like the recently installed Dual CT Scan.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has more than 200 cardiac doctors and 1600 employees who work together to manage over 14,500 admissions and 7,200emergency cases in a year.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital today has an infrastructure comprising of around 285 beds (it currently enjoys 100% occupancy rate), 5 Cath Labs besides a host of other world-class facilities.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute also offers facilities like One Stop Shop for Counselling, Admission and Discharge, Overnight Attendant Lounge, ATM, Parking, Valet Parking, Pharmacy, Emerald Lounge, International Services Desk, Corporate Desk, Business Centre.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital provides Airport Pickup Services to the International patients for a seem less experience and also take care of their dietary needs with different vegetarian and non-vegetarian cuisines.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are front office staffs at the reception who assists during the admission process.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There&rsquo;s also a insurance desk / TPA desk for the patients who are seeking the cashless route.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Escorts Heart Institute has tied-up with an elaborate group of insurance companies and TPAsso that the people can choose the best in healthcare, without worrying about the costs.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
