      '<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Care Institute of Medical Science (CIMS) is a multi super-speciality hospital with 350 beds. The hospital was founded by Dr. keyur Parikh in 2010. It is considered one of the best multi-speciality hospitals of Ahmadabad in Gujarat with more than 1000 employees. It provides a range of diagnostic and treatment services. The hospital offers the highest quality services and offers treatment to most diseases and medical problems with one of the highest success rates in India. The first successful heart transplant of Gujarat was done in this hospital. The surgery was conducted on 19 December 2016. It is a dedicated transplant centre for Heart, Liver, Kidney, Lung, and Paediatric Bone Marrow. The medical care facility was n CIMS offer treatments from the best doctors in the field of Cardiologist, Intervention Cardiologist, non-invasive Cardiology etc. The hospital is also seen as a booster for quality medical tourism to the region. CIMS is the only place in Gujarat to offer a combination of State-of-the-art Cardiac-Cathlab (fastest in the world with automatic &quot;7 second&quot; angiography) intensive care units, sleep lab, high-frequency ventilator for neonates, 8 OTs with 4 fully modular with LED lights (energy &amp; carbon savings), modular operation theatres with class 100 laminar air flow. The hospital offers diagnostic medical, surgical, palliative care facilities. CIMS provides financial aid and affordable healthcare to needy patients. The hospital is the only centre in India to be recognized as an American College of Cardiology (ACC) Centre of Excellence.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Specialisation </strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">CIMS has a specialised clinical department which includes Anaesthesiology, Cancer, Cardiac Surgery, Cardiology, Clinical Nutrition, Critical Care, Dentistry, Dermatology, E.N.T, Endocrinology, Gastroenterology, General Surgery, Genetics, Gl Surgery, Gynaecology &amp; Obstetrics, Health Check-Up, Heart Transplant, Infectious Disease, IVF, Liver Transplant, Neonatology &amp; Paediatrics, Nephrology, Neurology, Neurosurgery, Obesity, Ophthalmology, Orthopaedics/Joint Replacement, and Paediatric Bone Marrow</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Transplant, Pain Clinic, Physiotherapy &amp; Rehabilitation, Plastic Surgery, Pulmonology, Renal Transplant, Rheumatology, Sleep Medicine, Spine Surgery, Transplant Centre, Trauma Care, Urology, Vascular and Thoracic Surgery. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Critical care</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">There is a Critical Care Unit in CIMS which is headed by specialized internationally trained Intensivists who provide dedicated, continuous, specialized care to critically ill patients with a variety of medical or surgical conditions who require complex multi-organ support. The patients have 24-hour access to non-invasive and advanced mechanical ventilation, modern continuous invasive Hemodynamic monitoring systems and modern and efficient Radiology department. All this is backed by Consultants from the full range of Medical and Surgical Super Specialties</span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Some of the key features of Critical Care Unit are ECMO for refractory heart/lung failure, CRRT for renal failure with shock, High flow nasal cannula for respiratory failure, Transplant critical care, Neutropenic care, Oncology care, Paediatric care, Home care, E-ICU care (GE Centricity).</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Locality</strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">Care Institute of Medical Science is situated at Sola Gam Road, Science City, Panchamrut Bungalows, Ahmadabad, and Gujrat 380060. It is a 31 minute drive from the Ahmadabad Airport which is a distance of 24 kilometres. Shukan Mall is the nearest bus stop to the hospital which is at a 6 minute walking distance. Top rated hotel, Hotel Science City Inn is just 0.9 kilometres away from the hospital and Hotel Royal Blue is just 0.5 kilometres away. Tulin Inn Hotel and Hotel Sunshine are also nearby the hospital. Birmies, Shivala village garden, R Kitchen and Kuro - The Asian Bistro, Renaissance is some of the restaurants which are near to the hospital. You can explore Sabarmati Ashram, Sardar Vallabhbhai Patel National Memorial, Auto World Vintage Car Museum and Dada Harir Vav (Stepwell) which is nearby the hospital. Kamla Nehru Zoo, Teen Darwaza and Statue of Unity are some of the tourist attractions which are near to the hospital.</span></p>\r\n',
