      "<ul>\r\n\t<li>Asian Institute of Medical Sciences is equipped with 425 beds and provides preventive, diagnostic, therapeutic, rehabilitative, palliative and supportive services.</li>\r\n\t<li>The hospital has the largest number of critical care beds in the region with over 100 monitor beds.</li>\r\n\t<li>The ICU offers facilities for high end multi parameter monitoring and care manned round the clock by trained intensivists. The indoor air quality in the ICUs is supported by dedicated air supply units that keep the critical care free of any kind of contamination. The unit is backed by an efficient Laboratory and Radiology services and it comprises of round the clock consultant doctors cover, along with professionally trained nursing staff, that looks into the psychological and emotional requirements of the patient.</li>\r\n\t<li>There is an emergency unit at AIMS is located on the ground floor for convenient and swift access in case of an emergency. 24/7 Trauma Centre is a one-stop Accident Facility Centre, which is equipped to handle a range of medical crisis, from minor to critical emergencies, resuscitations in complex road traffic accidents. The emergencies are managed in a 15 bedded emergency care unit, looked after by an experienced team of doctors.</li>\r\n\t<li>There are dedicated elevators which ensure quick transfer of patients to operating rooms and ICUs.</li>\r\n\t<li>There is a round the clock ambulance services at this institute which provides 24/7 cover for trauma patients and has the best critical life-saving equipment on board.</li>\r\n\t<li>The hospital offers special services for the international patients which include Appointment Scheduling, A SIM card, provided to you immediately after your arrival, can take to your relatives home, VISA assistance, Treatment packages, Airport Pick-n-Drop facility, Hotel facility, if needed, Language interpreters, Foreign Exchange conversion, Fax, photocopy, and courier services, Laundry services, Express check-in through a dedicated International Patient&rsquo;s Lounge, Complimentary stay in your room for one attendant (while you are being operated on, you will be provided an alternative accommodation for your attendant), Choice of international cuisine, Internet access in the room, Dedicated international executive during your entire stay at &lsquo;AIMS&rsquo; for all your medical and non-medical needs, Ambulance pick-up, if required, Concierge services for dining and entertainment.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n",
