    about_hospital:
      '<p style="text-align:justify">Located in the heart of Navi Mumbai and established in 2007, the Fortis Hiranandani Hospital is one of the best multi-speciality hospitals and advanced tertiary care centres dedicated to more than 38 health departments. For over a decade, the hospital has been among the top hospitals and super speciality healthcare centres in the region of Navi Mumbai. Their well-equipped pathology laboratory has made their facility the only hospital with a NABL accredited pathology laboratory in Mumbai. The specialization of Fortis Hiranandani Hospital includes oncology, orthopaedics, cardiology, neurosciences, gynaecology, gastroenterology, internal medicine and nephrology. The hospital is on a mission to save and enrich lives while keeping in mind quality patient care and clinical excellence with compassion.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Specialisation </strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Fortis Hiranandani Hospital specialises in multiple areas including Bariatric &amp; Metabolic Surgery, Cardiology &amp; Cardiac Surgery, Clinical Departments, Dental Care, Dermatology, Diabetology &amp; Endocrinology, Emergency Medicine, Gastroenterology &amp; Gastrointestinal Surgeries, General &amp; Laparoscopic Surgery, Gynaecology &amp; Obstetrics, Haematology, Hepatology &amp; Liver Transplant, Intensive Care, Internal Medicine, Mental Health &amp; Behavioural Sciences, Nephrology, Neurology &amp;Neurosurgery, Oncology, Ophthalmology, Organ Transplant, Orthopaedic, Otolaryngology (ENT), Paediatrics &amp; Neonatology, Plastic &amp; Cosmetic Surgery, Pulmonology &amp; Sleep Medicine, Rheumatology, Robotic Surgery, Speciality clinics, Urology and Vascular Surgery.</p>\r\n\r\n<h3 style="text-align:justify"><strong>Location</strong></h3>\r\n\r\n<p style="text-align:justify">Fortis Hiranandani Hospital is located at Mini Sea Shore Road, Sector 10A, Vashi, Navi Mumbai, and Landmark: Opposite Mini Sea Shore. The closest metro stations to Fortis Hiranandani Hospital are- Vashi Sector No. 10-15 which is only 736 meters away and a 10 minute walk, whereas, Vashi Sector 4 is 1314 meters away, a 17 minute walk. The Chhatrapati Shivaji Maharaj International Airport is located near to the hospital with a distance of 21.6 kilometres which usually takes around 50 minutes to reach. Meluha the Fern, Radisson Mumbai Goregaon, Courtyard by Marriott Mumbai International Airport and HOTEL GRAND HERITAGE - Kurla West are some famous hotels in the locality. Masala Wok, The Loving Chef, Malvan Belly, Kebabs and Currys, Kolhapuri Mejwani, Everest Family Restaurants and The Food Studio are some restaurants in the vicinity of the hospital.</p>\r\n',
