    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Fortis Hiranandani Hospital received the National Energy Conservation Award from the honourable President of India himself.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital was also accredited with NABL (National Accreditation Board for Testing and Calibration Laboratories). It is the only hospital in Navi Mumbai with an SRL-NABL accredited pathology laboratory.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital was the first to get accredited by NABH (National Accreditation Board of Hospitals).</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Fortis Hiranandani Hospital was the first hospital in Navi Mumbai to be accredited by NABH for excellence in nursing (National Accreditation Board of Hospitals).</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Fortis Hiranandani Hospital is a 150-bed tertiary care advanced multispecialty hospital built over an area of 120,000 sq. ft.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Hiranandani Hospital has a dedicated emergency and casualty department providing 24/7 critical care services managed by a team of doctors who are available 24/7.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital is also equipped with state-of-the-art 4 major operation theatres (OT) and 1 minor Operation Theatre.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has treated over 5 lakh patients and has assured the best treatment for everyone.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Hiranandani Hospital has an experience of over 13 years an over 38 health departments more than 150 beds.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The multidisciplinary team of experts at Fortis Hospital, Navi Mumbai draws on the expertise of doctors, nurses, and other support staff available. The doctors are recognised all over the world for their expertise in the prevention, diagnosis, and treatment of complex and routine illnesses.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital is also equipped with a super ICU for providing emergency medical care to patients who are critically ill.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The critical care facility is supplemented with state-of-the-art facilities which facilitate faster diagnosis and efficient monitoring.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">As it is the only hospital with an SRL - NABL accredited pathology laboratory, it&rsquo;s pathology lab has established a niche place in the medical fraternity.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Fortis Hiranandani Hospital is efficiently equipped to conduct cosmetic surgery, bariatric surgery along with neuro and spine care.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
