    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with Best Intelligent Hospital award at AHPI Awards.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with Nursing Excellence (NABH), A recognition of the high quality of nursing care.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The first hospital in Mumbai to receive NABH-MIS accreditation.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded Hospital of The Year in Patent Care Award at CIMS Healthcare Excellence Awards 2021.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded as Best Hospital in Patient Care in CIMS Cardiology Speciality Award 2020.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with Prestigious Asia Pacific HIMSS Elsevier Digital Healthcare Award 2019</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with &quot;Most Popular Multi Specialty Hospital in India 2018 organised by Time Cyber Media.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital&rsquo;s state-of-the-art Imaging Centre is spanning over 10,000 square feet, houses 3 Tesla 32 channel wide bore Magnetic Resonance Imaging (MRI) scanner with MR guided Focused Ultrasound Surgery (MRgFUS) and High-Intensity-Focused-Ultrasound, 64 slice Positron Emission Tomography&ndash;Computed Tomography (PET CT) with cardiac capability.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">It has a total of 350 beds, 75 Critical Care Beds, 11 OTs, 350 eminent consultants, 100 resident doctors, 475 nursing staff and 1500 employees. It is the largest private sector hospital in Mumbai. The hospital is well-equipped with hospital rooms, state-of-the-art departments and technologically advanced systems.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Bariatric Surgery (Weight Loss Surgery) at Nanavati is one of the largest program in the region.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The Hospital also has the region&rsquo;s largest medical post-graduation program with over 70 seats in DNB and CPS aimed to create well-trained, ethical, skilled, resourceful leaders dedicated to the passion of healing that will empower the future medical fraternity.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has three basements that accommodate mechanised parking stacks, support services, and an elaborate Radiation Oncology department with a lineup of three state-of-the-art services.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are 17 high-speed elevators for a seamless operation on the planning front.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has state-of-the-art equipment such as the Pneumatic chutes, a fully integrated BMS and high infection control finishes.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The indoor air quality is regulated by large windows that maximize daylight, also facilitated by an airy central courtyard to allow air.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The refuge area at the fifth-floor level is designed as a therapeutic healing space that attempts to lift and revitalize the minds of the patient and the relative.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital provides Transportation service which includes Airport pickup, Hotels pickup, Local tourism options, Local transportation booking, Visa / Travel office, Car Hire, Private driver / Limousine services, Shopping trip organization,</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
