    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">L H Hiranandani Hospital has won the national level prestigious award : CIMS HealthCare Excellence Awards 2021.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">&nbsp;Dr L H Hiranandani Hospital has won International Hospital Federation awards(IHF) 2021 &ndash; for the project Primary Angioplasty in Myocardial Infarction (PAMI) &ndash;Achieving Excellence at the 2021 IHF Awards Ceremony IHF Barcelona.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Appreciation for Energy conservation and Green living in recognition of leadership in sustainability by TATA Power.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Most Caring Hospital Award Proudly Presented to Dr L H Hiranandani Hospital, In recognition of outstanding dedication, tireless, remarkable effort and commitment.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Certification by CII WR Task force on healthcare in association with Hosmac India Pvt Ltd and Conserve Consultant Pvt. Ltd 23rd Nov 2019.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">LH Hiranandani Hospital has received IMC Ram Krishna Bajaj National Quality Award for Excellence in Health Care.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital&rsquo;s Blood Bank received NABH accreditation in the year 2011.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Received AHPI award for Quality beyond Accreditation.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has well equipped ambulances. These ambulances are equipped with advanced life support systems which carry a doctor on board for cardiac and other life threatening emergencies. The task is to retrieve emergency cases from the proximity areas of the hospital.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are a total of 6 fully equipped operation theatres in the hospital with advanced Anaesthesia machines and state of the art anaesthesia equipment.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has an Auditorium located in the basement floor to conduct seminars, medical conferences and workshops. The auditorium has the capacity to host up to 80 participants.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There&rsquo;s a multi-purpose hall in the hospital located on the 13<sup>th</sup> floor which is used for conducting mid size medical conferences, clinical workshops, and live surgical demonstrations. The multi-purpose hall has the capacity of up to 200 people.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are a total of two pharmacies in the hospital. The main pharmacy store is located at the basement of the hospital whereas the day and night retail pharmacy is located at the ground floor.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There&rsquo;s an ATM service in the hospital available at the ground floor. The ATM service is provided by AXIS bank.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are two different cafeterias in the hospital which anyone can visit. The first cafeteria is on the ground floor which is run by the ISS catering services that also cater to the hospital. This cafeteria caters all forms of snacks and meals. The second cafeteria is the famous Coffee Day Express (Caf&eacute; coffee day chain). You can also get a panoramic view of the Powai Lake there while you enjoy coffee, tea, or any other beverage.&nbsp;</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There&rsquo;s a Day Care complex on the 10<sup>th</sup> floor of the hospital. The day care complex has a total of 9 beds with high end electronic monitoring systems. It also has a dedicated team of highly trained nurses who help in managing the department. It has it&rsquo;s own changing room and is operational from 8 AM to 8 PM.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital also offers the facility of Gymnasium which is located on the second floor of the hospital. The gymnasium has a professional trainer to help you and the membership cost is Rs. 1430/- per month.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There&rsquo;s a family lounge on the 11<sup>th</sup> floor of the hospital that is meant for the patients and relatives to spend some time together socially, surf the internet, read newspaper and have tea or coffee.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
