    awards:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with &ldquo;Best Multi-specialty Hospital Western Region Award&rdquo; at ET Health Awards 2021.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Awarded with &ldquo;Best Multi-speciality Hospital in Mumbai&rdquo; at NavaBharat Healthcare Awards 2021.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Ranked No. 1 Multi-specialty Hospital in Mumbai and the Western Region by The Week Magazine - 6th year in a row.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Excellence in Multi-specialty Hospital Award at the India Today Excellence Healthcare Awards 2018.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Kokilaben Hospital received the Univants of Healthcare Excellence 2020 Certificate of Achievement.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Kokilaben Hospital was awarded Best Multi-speciality Hospital - National, Best Hospital for Oncology and Dialectology - Western India at ET Health world Hospital Awards 2020.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Ranked No. 1 Multi-specialty Hospital in Mumbai and the Western Region by The Times of India - 3rd Time in a row.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Centre for Excellence Award for Neurology at the India Healthcare and Wellness Awards.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
    facilities:
      '<ul>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Kokilaben Dhirubhai Ambani Hospital is the only hospital in Mumbai with Full Time Specialist System (FTSS) which ensures easy access and availability of dedicated specialists. The entire specialist team is committed to provide the finest healthcare to each and every patient.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">A suite with an area of 750 square feet with exclusive entrances, terrace garden, visitor area, guest room and private terraces.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are a total of 30 elevators in the hospital which makes it the largest elevator bank in India capable of transporting 7,500 persons per hour. There are different elevators for inpatients, outpatients, staff and catering.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">There are a total of over 240 independent consulting clinics which have a capacity to handle over 9,000 outpatient consultations everyday.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has a laboratory which is housed on a single floor spread over an area of over 40,000 square feet. It offers highly advanced diagnostic, genetic and molecular biology tests and will serve as a referral centre for second opinions.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">It accommodates over 750 inpatient beds which allows optimal utilisation of resources and also ensures dignity, privacy, comfort and convenience to every patient.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">The hospital has 1 million square feet of space, 17 floors, 2 basements and 140+ OPD clinics, diagnostics and day care services.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">A nurse call system in single rooms, Twin rooms, general wards and ICUs.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Aquatic treadmill for sports and neurological rehabilitation.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">3 Tesla MRIs</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">40 Slice PET CT, SPECT and 64 Slice Dual Source CT.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">A convention centre with a capacity of 70-500+ that also provides a facility of live audio and video for seminars.</li>\r\n\t<li style="text-align:justify">Some of the other services include Pharmacy, beauty salon, ATM, food court, fine dining restaurant, and patient resource centre.</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n',
