    about_hospital:
      '<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">Manipal Hospitals is one of India&#39;s best multi-specialty healthcare providers catering to both Indian and international patients. It is a part of the Manipal Education and Medical Group (MEMG), a leader in the areas of education and healthcare. Their log is &ldquo;Pragyanam Brahma&rdquo; which means &ldquo;Knowledge is Life&rdquo;, which defines the quality of healthcare provided at the Manipal Hospitals or their institution. The hospital is devoted towards clinical excellence, patient-centricity, and ethical practices. It offers an integrated range of healthcare services from out-patient treatment and diagnostics to advanced clinical care which also extends to personalised home-care services. The hospital is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities on par with global standards.It deliver the most cutting edge treatments, starting from the simplest to the most complex medical problems. There are 4 branches of Manipal Hospitals in Bangalore, which are, Manipal Hospital Bangalore, Old Airport Road, Manipal North side Hospital, Bangalore, Malleshwaram, Dr. Malathi Manipal Hospital Bangalore Jayanagar, and Manipal Hospital Whitefield. </span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,"><strong>Specialisation </strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,">Manipal Hospital, Old Airport Road has specialised departments for different treatments including general surgery, ENT, Anesthesia, pulmonology, plastic and reconstructive surgery, rheumatology, vascular surgery, Infectious diseases, Geriatrics, dermatology, dentistry, bariatric surgery, endocrinology, ICU and critical care, ophthalmology, haematology, hemato-oncology, neonatology, and rehabilitation services.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,">Manipal Hospital Whitefield has specialised departments which includes Cardiology, Cardiothoracic Vascular Surgery, Gastrointestinal Science, Nephrology, Neurology, Neurosurgery, Obstetrics and Gynaecology, Organ Transplant, Orthopedics, Paediatric And Child Care, Rheumatology, Spine Care, Urology, Cancer Care, ermatology, Diabetes and Endocrinology, Ear Nose Throat, Fetal Medicine, General Medicine, General Surgery, ICU and Critical Care, Infectious Disease, Internal Medicine, IVF and Infertility, Laparoscopic Surgery, Liver Transplantation Surgery, Microbiology, Neonatology &amp; NICU, Accident and Emergency Care, Anesthesiology, Bariatric Surgery, Clinical Psychology, Dental Medicine, Nutrition And Dietetics, Ophthalmology, Pain Medicine , Pathology, Pharmacy, Physiotherapy, Plastic And Cosmetic Surgery, Podiatric Surgery, Psychiatry, Psychology, Pulmonology (Respiratory and Sleep Medicine), Radiology.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,">Some of the speciality departments of Manipal Hospital Malleshwaram are Urology, Nephrology, Neurology, Paediatric surgery, Laparoscopic surgery, Neonatology, Gastroenterology, Joint Replacement &amp; Arthroscopy, Plastic surgery, Surgical Oncology, Spine surgery &amp; state of the art INTENSIVE CARE UNIT.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,">Some of the speciality departments of Manipal Hospital Jayanagar are Appendicitis, Varicose Veins, Hysteroscopy Procedures, Spine Surgeries, TURP, Pregnancy &amp; Child Birth, Myomectomy, Laparoscopic assisted vaginal hysterectomy (LAVH), Cystectomy, Laparascopic, Hysteroscopic Surgeries, Hysterectomy Vaginal and Abdominal, Percutaneous, Dialysis, Urological Surgeries for Kidney, Ureter, Bladder stones, Urological surgeries, Tummy tuck, Breast Augmentation, Rhinoplasty, Liposuction, Reconstructive Surgery, All procedures across Dermatology, Pulmonology, Rheumatology, Endocrinology, ENT, Nephrology Urology, Surgical Gastroenterology.</span></span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="font-family:Calibri,"><strong>Locality</strong></span></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11.0pt">Manipal Hospital is situated at 98, HAL Old Airport Road, Kodihalli, Bangalore, Karnataka, 560017. The distance from the hospital to Bangalore Airport is 41 kilometres which takes 1 hour 5 minutes to cover depending on the traffic conditions. The nearest Railway station to the Hospital is (KJM) Krishna Rajapuram Station which is at a distance of 5.9 kilometres. Top rated Hotel, Hotel The Leela Palace is just 0.4 kilometre away from the hospital and Hotel Treebu Trend Greenwood Premier Suits is just 0.5 kilometre away. Bloom Hotel and Starlings Mac Hotel and Suits are also close to the hospital. Jamavar, Library Bar, Le Cirque Signature and Cloudy are some of the restaurants which are near the hospital. You can explore Shiva Temple, Domlur Oneness Centre and Lalbagh Botanical Garden which are close to the hospital. ISKCON Temple, Bangalore Palace and Thottikallu Falls are some of the tourist attractions which are near the hospital.</span></p>\r\n',
