    doctor_brief:
      '<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Dr. Prochi Madon is currently an Honorary Consultant Geneticist at Mumbai&#39;s Jaslok Hospital and Research Centre&#39;s Department of Assisted Reproduction and Genetics. She has almost 19 years of expertise as an IVF specialist. She attends and presents papers at genetics conferences both nationally and internationally. Jaslok&#39;s Genetics and PGD laboratory is noted for its thorough visual reports. The Department of Assisted Reproduction and Genetics reported the first live births in India following PGD by FISH for translocations and inversions.</span></p>\r\n\r\n<h3><span style="font-size:11pt"><strong>Specialised Treatments </strong></span></h3>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Dr. Madon is an internationally recognised genetics expert. Her interests include the following:</span></p>\r\n\r\n<ul>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Infertility and recurrent miscarriages</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Cytogenetics</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Delayed puberty and hypogonadism</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Congenital malformations</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Developmental delay and autism spectrum disorders</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Prenatal samples</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">Products of conception</span></li>\r\n\t<li><span style="font-size:11pt">PGD in embryos for translocations and inversions</span></li>\r\n</ul>\r\n\r\n<p><span style="font-size:11pt">She is also known for performing specialised treatments which include IVF, Intracytoplasmic Sperm Injection Procedure ICSI, Intrauterine Insemination, Ovulation Induction Procedure, Egg Donation, Embryo Donation, Frozen Embryo Transfer (FET), ransvaginal Oocyte Retrieval (TVOR) (Oocyte Retrieval), Oocyte Cryopreservation, Human Egg Bank, Egg Freezing, Laser Assisted Hatching (LAH) Procedure, Tubal Embryo Transfer Procedure, Peritoneal Oocyte and Sperm Transfer, GIFT and ZIFT Procedure, Blastocyst Culture and Transfer, Cryopreservation, Ovarian Drilling, Therapeutic Donor Insemination, Fertility Surgeries, Fibroid Removal Surgery, Myomectomy Surgery, Operative Laparoscopy, Hysteroscopy, Laparoscopic Vaginal, Hysterectomy, Laparoscopic supra, cervical Hysterectomy, Total Laparoscopic Hysterectomy, and Laparoscopic Tubal Ligation.</span></p>\r\n',
    doc_rating: "5",
