    picture:
      "https://www.globalmvt.com/upload/doctor/1653404871_dr._n._k._pandey.jpg",
    doctor_brief:
      '<p><span style="font-size:11pt">Dr. Narendra Kumar Pandey is a visionary with a quick wit and sharp intellect. His family instilled in him a strong work ethic, which, together with his dedication, hard effort, and high ethical standards, has helped him become a renowned surgeon. Dr. NK Pandey, the honorary recipient of the Padma Shri Award for his remarkable contribution to the field of healthcare, founded Asian Institute of Medical Sciences.Dr. N K Pandey has extensive and varied experience in the healthcare field, having held a number of distinguished roles over his career.Dr. Pandey was crucial in the establishment of various National Board of Examination Specialty Diploma Courses, including Respiratory Medicine Surgery, Intensive Care, and others. Dr. Pandey has also served as an Examiner for the Royal College of Surgeons of Edinburgh, both for the MRCS and FRCS, since 2000. He is also a member of the Chicago Council of the International College of Surgeons. Dr. Pandey served as the Joint Editor of the Indian Journal of Surgery, an indexed journal published by the Association of Surgeons of India and sent to over 20,000 people worldwide.</span></p>\r\n',
